This file is a placeholder for the decision audit chain diagram.

Recommended diagram content:
- Horizontal chain of blocks (like a blockchain)
- Each block contains: Step, Action, GSAI Score, State Hash, Parent Hash
- Arrows connecting blocks via parent_hash → hash links
- Color coding: green for accepted, red for rejected decisions

For generation:
- Use draw.io / Excalidraw / Mermaid
- Output as PNG at 1400×300px

Mermaid equivalent:
```mermaid
flowchart LR
    B0[Step 0\nInit State\nHash: a1b2...] --> B1[Step 1\nSYNC\nHash: c3d4...]
    B1 --> B2[Step 2\nRECOVER\nHash: e5f6...]
    B2 --> B3[Step 3\nNOOP ⛔\nHash: e5f6...]
    B2 --> B4[Step 3\nRECOVER\nHash: g7h8...]
```
